    <p>
     Languages
    </p>
    <ul>
     <li>
      <script src="https://s2.pstatp.com/cdn/expire-1-M/js-cookie/2.2.0/js.cookie.min.js" type="application/javascript">
      </script>
      <script>
       function changeUserLang(langCode) { 
var params = { action: 'options', change: 'language=' + langCode, format: 'json'};
api = new mw.Api();
api.postWithToken( 'csrf', params ).done( function( data ) {
    window.location.reload();
});
}

function changeAnonLang(langCode) { 
    Cookies.set('ak_aklanguage', langCode);
    window.location.reload();
}

function changeLang(langCode){
    var username = mw.config.get("wgUserName");
    if ( !!username ) {
        changeUserLang( langCode );
    }
    else {
        changeAnonLang( langCode );
    }
}
      </script>
      <a id="switcher-ja" onclick="changeLang('ja')">
       日本語
      </a>
     </li>
     <li>
      <a id="switcher-en" onclick="changeLang('en')">
       English
      </a>
     </li>
     <li>
      <a id="switcher-zh-cn" onclick="changeLang('zh-cn')">
       中文
      </a>
     </li>
    </ul>
